summary:
Mathilde Grenod is a French integrated producer for documentary, commercial & photography campaigns, based in Amsterdam and the South of France.

From agency production at Dentsu Creative Amsterdam and VIRTUE to line production at VICE, she’s been giving life to projects with amour in Dutch, English and French.  

● Documentary series produced for: VICE • Rakuten TV. 
● Clients include:  Google • Coca Cola • Borjomi • Orangina • Fiat • Porsche • Volkswagen• Mazda • L’Oréal Paris • Puma • Marschall • Pearle. 
● Press & Awards: It’s Nice That • Vogue • TechCrunch • The FWA • BFM TV  • France Inter • Skateism • Webby Awards.

Feel free to get in touch at mathildegrenod@gmail.com for any questions or meetings requests.
